ABOUT

Advanced card search for hearthstone in the style of magiccards.info.

Allows searches like this:

  race:dragon AND r:legendary AND attack>10

  playable:paladin AND cost<=3 AND text:secret

  type:minion AND text:taunt

If you just want to use the card search it's running at:

  http://hs.bluebones.net/

SETUP

- Copy config.json.example to config.json and update with your values.
- $ composer install
- $ php -f classes/setup.php
- $ php -f classes/loader.php

